    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Chairs of various designs, positioned at the front of certain Protestant churches and used by the preacher during services. For chairs having a tall back surmounted by a lectern and used as a  pulpit, use "preaching chairs."</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
